                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary>
                            This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 1b (as <persName ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/76627502">Pormann</persName> and <persName>Joosse</persName> point out, it has a longer version of the introduction);
                            the beginning of each Book is as follows:
                            Bk 1: 2b; Bk 2: 15a; Bk 3: 34b; Bk 4: 50a; Bk 5: 78b; Bk 6: 101a; Bk 7: 116b.
                        </summary>
                       
